<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL1">
<l>kāvaliṟ pulaṉai vaittuk kalitaṉaik kaṭakkap pāyntu,</l>
<l>nāvaliṭ ṭuḻitaru kiṉṟōm namaṉtamar talaikaḷ mītē,</l>
<l>mūvula kuṇṭu miḻnta mutalvaniṉ nāmaṅ kaṟṟa</l>
<l>āvalip puṭaimai kaṇṭāya raṅkamā nakaru ḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O First Cause who swallowed and spit out the three worlds!</l>
<l rend="indent">[Due to our] possessing the pride of having learnt Your names,</l>
<l rend="indent">We have kept the senses under guard;</l>
<l rend="indent">We leapt across sins/the kali-age;</l>
<l rend="indent">And shouting ‘Victory!’,</l>
<l rend="indent">We wander about on the very heads of Yama’s people!</l>
<l>Look, o You who are in the big city of Raṅgam!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
